ношении ТСЖ &quot;ВЕСТА&quot;будут применены меры административного воздействия.</p><p>Приложение: Уведомление.</p>","author_name":"Администрация Невского района","performer":null,"response_performers":[],"files":[{"id":18363658,"url":"/storage/2/de3297a3-6a8b-4890-a894-29f108b3e2b0.pdf","original_name":"Увед.  по проблеме № 3265278 от 23.03.2021 1.pdf"}],"photos":[],"reject":null,"interim_date":"2021-04-26"},"meta":{"title":"Ответ","icon_text":"ПО","icon_title":"Промежуточный ответ","bg_color":"#E3F2FD","border_color":"#536DFE","status_font_color":"#FFFFFF","status_bg_color":"#A5D6A7","icon_bg_color":"#536DFE"},"content_type":28},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13351177","payload":{"id":13351177,"dt":"2021-03-13T14:05:23.109976","status_name":"Рассмотрение","status":3},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-clock-o","icon_bg_color":"#FCAA62"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13346637","payload":{"id":13346637,"dt":"2021-03-12T22:14:13.967555","status_name":"Модерация","status":1},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-hand-paper-o","icon_bg_color":"#469ED3"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.petition","key":"petition_3617620","payload":{"id":3617620,"dt":"2021-03-12T22:14:13.841000","status_name":"Промежуточный ответ","body":[{"text":"Пропаганда либо незаконная реклама наркотических средств, психотропных веществ или их прекурсоров","typeof":1}],"photos":[{"url":"/storage/1/db43a4fa-9f52-4c4f-a45d-6dc76d34fe5e.jpg","original_name":"20210312_155419-1.jpg","id":4092553,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/83/99/83991cf89406723e3b6e47443e59840f.jpg","original_url":"/storage/1/ec9a5c1d-531b-41bd-a14e-c70cb8c4793f.jpg","size":"946x699"},{"url":"/storage/1/8babe400-89c0-4732-bcf3-929a698f71d8.jpg","original_name":"20210312_155342-1.jpg","id":4092554,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/89/88/8988bf1d57c445ecfea843a7db9f66f6.jpg","original_url":"/storage/1/8babe400-89c0